nodes.text: Dormitz was an individual who served in the military branch of the militant political faction known as the First Order, successor of the Galactic Empire. Holding the rank of lieutenant, Dormitz worked as a pilot and at one point flew an Upsilon-class command shuttle.
Dormitz was first mentioned on a card in the Upsilon-class Shuttle Expansion Pack released by Fantasy Flight Games for their Star Wars: X-Wing Miniatures Game on February 2, 2017.
